[[File:The_Tank_exterior,_September_2018.jpg|thumb]]的外外百老汇剧院]]

'''外外百老汇'''（{{Lang-en|Off-Off-Broadway}}）是指位于[[美国|美国]][[纽约市|纽约市]]的一些规模比[[百老汇|百老汇]]及[[外百老汇|外百老汇]]剧院更小的剧院，通常只有不到100个座位。外外百老汇运动是1958年反商业和[[實驗劇場|实验性]]或[[前衛|前卫性]]戏剧和舞台剧运动的一部分。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Charles Wright |title=Off-Off-Broadway, Way Back When |url=https://www.theatermania.com/new-york/news/off-off-broadway-way-back-when_5191.html |publisher=TheaterMania |accessdate=2022-05-30 |language=en |date=2004-10-04 |archive-date=2018-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181202232752/https://www.theatermania.com/new-york/news/off-off-broadway-way-back-when_5191.html }}</ref> 不过随着时间的推移，现在的一些外外百老汇作品已经脱离了其运动早期的实验精神。<ref name="McNamara">{{cite journal |author1=Brooks McNamara |title=Broadway: A Theatre Historian's Perspective |journal=The Drama Review |date=2001-12-01 |volume=45 |issue=4 |pages=125-128 |doi=10.1162/105420401772990360 |s2cid=57571738 |language=en}}</ref>

== 发展历史 ==
外外百老汇运动始于1958年，其宗旨在于“完全拒绝商业剧院”。<ref>{{Harvnb|Viagas|2004|p=72}}</ref> 迈克尔·史密斯（{{lang|en|Michael Smith}}）将这个名词的发明归功于杰瑞·高默（{{lang|en|Jerry Tallmer}}）。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Michael Smith |title=The Good Scene: Off Off-Broadway |journal={{Link-en|TDR (期刊)|TDR (journal)|杜兰戏剧评论}} |date=1966 |volume=10 |issue=4 |pages=159 - 176 |doi=10.2307/1125218 |jstor=1125218 |language=en}}</ref> 很快，第一批“外外百老汇”剧场在[[格林尼治村|格林尼治村]]的咖啡馆中出现，尤其是位于柯尼利亚街31号的{{Link-en|西诺咖啡馆|Caffe Cino}}。西诺咖啡馆由{{Link-en|乔·西诺|Joe Cino}}经营，他很早就对演员和剧作家表示欢迎并同意他们在自己的场地里上演戏剧，而且他不会事先去了解戏剧剧本，甚至不会去了解剧本的内容。而西诺咖啡馆的DIY美学也影响了剧作家和导演们，他们开始尝试利用废弃物品进行再开发，利用附近街道废弃的物品来制作舞台背景。<ref>{{Harvnb|Malewitz|2014|p=51}}</ref> {{Link-en|拉马马实验剧团|La MaMa Experimental Theatre Club}}的{{Link-en|艾伦·斯图尔特|Ellen Stewart}}和位于[[耶德逊纪念教堂|耶德逊纪念教堂]]内[[耶德逊纪念教堂|耶德逊诗人剧场]]的{{Link-en|阿尔·卡明斯|Al Carmines}}也是外外百老汇崛起的重要人物。其他上演过大量外外百老汇戏剧的著名剧场还有{{Link-en|创世纪剧院|Theatre Genesis}}、纽约剧场组合（{{lang|en|New York Theatre Ensemble}}）、<ref>{{cite magazine |date=1970-03-02 |editor1-last=Gilbert |editor1-first=Ruth |title=In and Around Town |url=https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=hscDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA13&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false |magazine=[[紐約_(雜誌)|纽约]] |language=en |publisher=New York Media, LLC |volume=3 |issue=9 |page=13 |issn=0028-7369 |access-date=2022-05-31 |archive-date=2022-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531030256/https://books.google.co.jp/books?id=hscDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA13&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref> 老可靠剧场（{{lang|en|The Old Reliable}}）、<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Stephen J. Bottoms |title=Playing Underground: A Critical History of the 1960s Off-Off-Broadway Movement |date=2004 |doi=10.3998/mpub.22965 |isbn=9780472031948 |publisher=University of Michigan Press |language=en}}</ref> 多芬剧场（{{lang|en|The Dove Company}}）、剧作家工坊（{{lang|en|The Playwrights Workshop}}）<ref>{{cite web |title=Robert Patrick Papers ca. 1940-1984 |url=https://www.nypl.org/sites/default/files/archivalcollections/pdf/thepatri.pdf |publisher=The New York Public Library |language=en |date=2004-05 |access-date=2022-05-31 |archive-date=2022-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531030253/https://www.nypl.org/sites/default/files/archivalcollections/pdf/thepatri.pdf }}</ref> 和演员艺术工作室（{{lang|en|Workshop of the Players Art}}）<ref>{{cite web |author1=Tony Ortega |title=Christopher Lloyd! Stacy Keach! Jessica Tandy! It’s the 1973 Obies! |url=https://www.villagevoice.com/2011/05/03/christopher-lloyd-stacy-keach-jessica-tandy-its-the-1973-obies/ |publisher={{Link-en|乡村之声|The Village Voice}} |accessdate=2022-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710010213/https://www.villagevoice.com/2011/05/03/christopher-lloyd-stacy-keach-jessica-tandy-its-the-1973-obies/ |archivedate=2018-07-18 |language=en |date=2011-05-04}}</ref> 等。

在外外百老汇被合并之前，外外百老汇戏剧以其实验性质闻名。{{Link-en|布鲁克斯·麦克纳马拉|Brooks McNamara}}写道，随着时间的推移，外外百老汇的作品开始失去其的一些实验精神，并反而开始模仿“外百老汇的特点，逐渐朝着百老汇的形象特点来重塑自己，尽管它们制作的作品经常不适合商业剧院”。<ref name="McNamara" />

那些以{{Link-en|演员权益协会|Actors' Equity Association}}成员为主要角色的外外百老汇戏剧作品可能更像是该协会的演示案例，旨在让未来的潜在雇主认识其旗下演员。演员权益协会尊重制作此类作品所需要的相关工会规则，包括对演出门票价格、排练时间及演出时间的限制。<ref>{{cite web |title=NY Showcase |url=https://www.actorsequity.org/resources/contracts/Showcase-NY/ |publisher={{Link-en|演员权益协会|Actors' Equity Association}} |language=en |access-date=2022-05-31 |archive-date=2022-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220610185907/https://www.actorsequity.org/resources/contracts/Showcase-NY/ }}</ref> 事实上，专业演员也会参与这类演示案例作品的制作，并构成了大多数纽约演员的舞台工作。而与此同时，修订《演员权益协会演出案例规则》的运动正在进行，相关人员认为该规则过于严厉而导致不利于纽约剧院的复兴。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Garrett Eisler |title=Breaking the Code? |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/theater/0735%2Ceisler%2C77610%2C11.html |publisher={{Link-en|乡村之声|The Village Voice}} |accessdate=2022-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071109084522/http://www.villagevoice.com/theater/0735,eisler,77610,11.html |archivedate=2007-11-09 |language=en |date=2007-08-28}}</ref>

1964年，外外百老汇作品获得了参与{{Link-en|奥比奖|Obie Award}}的评选资格。1974年，[[戏剧桌奖|戏剧桌奖]]开始以同样的标准评选外外百老汇作品与百老汇作品、外百老汇作品。<ref>{{cite web |title=About the Drama Desk Awards |url=http://awards.dramadesk.org/about.html |publisher=[[戏剧桌奖|戏剧桌奖]] |accessdate=2022-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325074058/http://awards.dramadesk.org/about.html |archivedate=2015-03-25 |language=en}}</ref> 而自2005年以来，{{Link-en|纽约创新戏剧奖|New York Innovative Theatre Awards}}都会表彰在外外百老汇取得艺术成就的个人和组织。<ref>{{cite web |title=About The New York Innovative Theatre Awards |url=https://www.nyitawards.com/about |publisher={{Link-en|纽约创新戏剧奖|New York Innovative Theatre Awards}} |accessdate=2022-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123225853/https://www.nyitawards.com/about |archivedate=2021-11-23 |language=en}}</ref>

剧作家{{Link-en|柯克·伍德·布罗姆利|Kirk Wood Bromley}}在2005年的{{Link-en|纽约创新戏剧奖|New York Innovative Theatre Awards}}颁奖礼上建议用“独立剧院（{{lang|en|Independent Theatre}}{{\}}{{lang|en|Indie Theatre}}）”来取代“外外百老汇”。<ref>{{cite book |editor=Jeffrey Eric Jenkins |title=The Best Plays Theater Yearbook |date=2007 |publisher=Hal Leonard |isbn=9780879103460 |page=261 |edition=87th Edition |url=https://archive.org/details/bestplaystheater00jeff_1/page/261/mode/2up |accessdate=2022-06-01 |language=en}}</ref>

